ul.li: Atomic Context: Entire sequence must hold PagingLock
Error Handling: If Step 2 fails, abort and return E_IO

g.text: Sync Dirty/Ref bits from hardware to PTE

text.tspan: Data MUST be written to swap before pointers are cleared.
TLB must be flushed BEFORE Page Table Entry is cleared.
Clearing PTE triggers Page Faults for future access.
Marking in_use=false must be the LAST step.
